{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a Shopify Online Store 2.0 section featuring a clean, modern, and minimal Contact Us layout.
    
    ### Layout Requirements
    
    * Maximum content width: 1200px.
    * Section padding: 60px top and bottom.
    * Fully responsive across desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.
    * No footer elements, social media icons, or additional content below the section.
    * Desktop layout should use a two-column structure:
    
      * Contact Form on one side.
      * Image Block directly opposite the form.
    * Both columns should be vertically centered.
    * Recommended desktop ratio: 50/50 or 55/45.
    * On mobile, stack the image and form vertically with appropriate spacing.
    
    ### Image Block
    
    Add an image block opposite the contact form.
    
    Requirements:
    
    * Image selectable through Shopify theme editor using an image_picker setting.
    * Optional image alt text setting.
    * Image should fill its container while maintaining aspect ratio.
    * Rounded corners (optional setting or default 8px).
    * Responsive behavior with no distortion.
    * If no image is selected, display a subtle placeholder.
    
    ### Section Settings (Schema)
    
    Add the following customizable settings:
    
    1. Section Title (text)
    2. Background Color (color picker)
    3. Contact Image (image_picker)
    4. Image Alt Text (text)
    5. Button Label (text, default: "Send")
    6. Content Alignment (select)
    
       * Left
       * Center (default)
       * Right
    
    ### Alignment Behavior
    
    The Content Alignment setting should:
    
    * Control text alignment for:
    
      * Section title
      * Form labels
      * Success/error messages
      * Submit button
    * Control horizontal positioning of the form container using flexbox:
    
      * Left → justify-content: flex-start
      * Center → justify-content: center
      * Right → justify-content: flex-end
    
    ### Contact Form
    
    Use Shopify native form functionality:
    
    {% form 'contact' %}
    
    ### Form Fields
    
    1. Your Name (required)
    2. Your Email (required, email type)
    3. Subject
    4. Your Message (textarea, minimum height 180px)
    5. File Upload (single file input)
    6. Submit Button (uses editable button label)
    
    ### Form Functionality
    
    * Display Shopify validation errors.
    * Display success confirmation message after submission.
    * Use accessible labels for all fields.
    * Proper form field associations using for/id attributes.
    * Mobile-friendly and keyboard accessible.
    
    ### Styling
    
    #### Inputs
    
    * Full width
    * 1px solid #ccc border
    * 6px border radius
    * 12px padding
    * 15px spacing between fields
    * Clean, minimal appearance
    
    #### Textarea
    
    * Minimum height: 180px
    * Resizable vertically
    
    #### Button
    
    * Background: #000
    * Text color: #fff
    * Padding: 10px 24px
    * Border radius: 6px
    * Hover background: #333
    * Alignment follows Content Alignment setting
    
    ### Responsive Behavior
    
    Desktop:
    
    * Two-column layout with image opposite the form.
    * Equal height columns where possible.
    
    Tablet:
    
    * Reduced spacing while maintaining two-column layout if space permits.
    
    Mobile:
    
    * Single-column stacked layout.
    * Image displayed above the form.
    * Full-width inputs and button.
    
    ### Code Requirements
    
    * Use semantic HTML.
    * Use Shopify Liquid best practices.
    * Include complete schema.
    * No external libraries or dependencies.
    * Optimized, clean, production-ready code.
    
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-contact-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .ai-contact-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-contact-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 40px;
    text-align: {{ block.settings.content_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-contact-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ai-contact-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 400px;
  }

  .ai-contact-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .ai-contact-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 400px;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-contact-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-width: 300px;
    max-height: 300px;
  }

  .ai-contact-form-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    {% if block.settings.content_alignment == 'left' %}
      justify-content: flex-start;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_alignment == 'right' %}
      justify-content: flex-end;
    {% else %}
      justify-content: center;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-contact-form-inner-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-contact-form-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 15px;
  }

  .ai-contact-field-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-contact-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: {{ block.settings.content_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-contact-input-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-contact-textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-contact-file-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .ai-contact-textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    min-height: 180px;
    resize: vertical;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .ai-contact-button-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    {% if block.settings.content_alignment == 'left' %}
      justify-content: flex-start;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_alignment == 'right' %}
      justify-content: flex-end;
    {% else %}
      justify-content: center;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-contact-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 10px 24px;
    background-color: #000;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-contact-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: #333;
  }

  .ai-contact-success-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 12px;
    background-color: #d4edda;
    color: #155724;
    border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-align: {{ block.settings.content_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-contact-error-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 12px;
    background-color: #f8d7da;
    color: #721c24;
    border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-align: {{ block.settings.content_alignment }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .ai-contact-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .ai-contact-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .ai-contact-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .ai-contact-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      min-height: 300px;
    }

    .ai-contact-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      min-height: 300px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<contact-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-contact-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-contact-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.section_title != blank %}
      <h2 class="ai-contact-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.section_title }}</h2>
    {% endif %}

          <div class="ai-contact-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.contact_image %}
          <img
            src="{{ block.settings.contact_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
            alt="{{ block.settings.image_alt_text | escape }}"
            loading="lazy"
            width="{{ block.settings.contact_image.width }}"
            height="{{ block.settings.contact_image.height }}"
            class="ai-contact-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
        {% else %}
          <div class="ai-contact-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
          </div>
        {% endif %}<div class="ai-contact-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">

      </div>

      <div class="ai-contact-form-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <div class="ai-contact-form-inner-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% form 'contact' %}
            <div class="ai-contact-form-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if form.posted_successfully? %}
                <div
                  class="ai-contact-success-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  id="ai-contact-success-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                  Thank you for contacting us. We'll get back to you as soon as possible.
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              {% if form.errors %}
                <div
                  class="ai-contact-error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  id="ai-contact-error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                  Please correct the errors below and try again.
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              <div class="ai-contact-field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <label for="ai-contact-name-{{ ai_gen_id }}" class="ai-contact-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  Your Name <span aria-label="required">*</span>
                </label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="ai-contact-name-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[name]"
                  class="ai-contact-input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  value="{{ form.name }}"
                  required
                  {% if form.errors contains 'name' %}
                    aria-invalid="true"
                    aria-describedby="ai-contact-error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  {% endif %}
                >
              </div>

              <div class="ai-contact-field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <label for="ai-contact-email-{{ ai_gen_id }}" class="ai-contact-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  Your Email <span aria-label="required">*</span>
                </label>
                <input
                  type="email"
                  id="ai-contact-email-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[email]"
                  class="ai-contact-input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  value="{{ form.email }}"
                  autocomplete="email"
                  autocorrect="off"
                  autocapitalize="off"
                  required
                  {% if form.errors contains 'email' %}
                    aria-invalid="true"
                    aria-describedby="ai-contact-error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  {% endif %}
                >
              </div>

              <div class="ai-contact-field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <label for="ai-contact-subject-{{ ai_gen_id }}" class="ai-contact-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  Subject
                </label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="ai-contact-subject-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[subject]"
                  class="ai-contact-input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  value="{{ form.subject }}"
                >
              </div>

              <div class="ai-contact-field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <label for="ai-contact-message-{{ ai_gen_id }}" class="ai-contact-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  Your Message
                </label>
                <textarea
                  id="ai-contact-message-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[body]"
                  class="ai-contact-textarea-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >{{ form.body }}</textarea>
              </div>

              <div class="ai-contact-field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <label for="ai-contact-file-{{ ai_gen_id }}" class="ai-contact-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  File Upload
                </label>
                <input
                  type="file"
                  id="ai-contact-file-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[file]"
                  class="ai-contact-file-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
              </div>

              <div class="ai-contact-button-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <button type="submit" class="ai-contact-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ block.settings.button_label }}
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endform %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</contact-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class ContactSection{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        const successMessage = this.querySelector('#ai-contact-success-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        if (successMessage) {
          successMessage.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
        }
      }
    }

    customElements.define('contact-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}', ContactSection{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Contact us",
  "tag": null,
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Section"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "section_title",
      "label": "Section title",
      "default": "Get in Touch"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "background_color",
      "label": "Background color",
      "default": "#ffffff"
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "content_alignment",
      "label": "Content alignment",
      "options": [
        {
          "value": "left",
          "label": "Left"
        },
        {
          "value": "center",
          "label": "Center"
        },
        {
          "value": "right",
          "label": "Right"
        }
      ],
      "default": "center"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Image"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "contact_image",
      "label": "Contact image"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "image_alt_text",
      "label": "Image alt text"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Form"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "button_label",
      "label": "Button label",
      "default": "Send"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Contact us"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
